        "text_LGGTqD": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The autonomic nervous system (ANS) regulates heart rate, breathing, vascular tone, perspiration, and stress adaptation.</p><p>When stress or imbalance occurs, subtle changes in microcirculation and skin conductivity take place. These variations influence electro-photonic emissions at the fingertips.</p><p>Bio-Well captures these changes and translates them into measurable indicators of regulatory balance.</p>",
